---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

import Text from '../components/system/Text.astro';
import BigAdmissionCTA from '../components/BigAdmissionCTA.astro';

import clubsBGimage from '../images/clubs/clubsBGImage.jpeg';

import Button from '../components/system/Button.astro';

import TopNavigationBar from '../components/TopNavigationBar.astro';
import AdmissionMarquee from '../components/campus/admissionMarquee.astro';

import '../global.css'
import GalleryMarquee from '../components/campus/galleryMarquee.astro';
import Footer from '../components/landingPage/Footer.astro';

import preeti from '../images/aboutUs/preeti.png'
import sowmia from '../images/aboutUs/sowmia.png'
import vittal from '../images/aboutUs/vittal.png'
import missionCardBG from '../images/aboutUs/missionCardBG.png'
import cupIcon from '../images/aboutUs/CupIcon.svg'
import art from '../images/clubs/art.png'
import debate from '../images/clubs/debate.png'
import eco from '../images/clubs/eco.png'
import firstFoot from '../images/clubs/firstFoot.png'
import heritage from '../images/clubs/heritage.png'
import math from '../images/clubs/math.png'
import scouts from '../images/clubs/scouts.png'
import science from '../images/clubs/science.png'
import literary from '../images/clubs/literary.png'

---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <main class="flex flex-col h-screen w-screen relative bg-white">
    <div 
      class="flex-1 main-container h-screen w-screen"
      style={{
        overflowY: 'overlay',
        overflowX: 'hidden',
      }}
    >
      <div class='flex flex-col bg-white'>
        <TopNavigationBar />
        <div class='h-[72.6px] w-full bg-black'>
        </div>
  
        <div class='min-h-[350px] max-h-[350px] w-full flex justify-center items-center flex-col max-md:min-h-[350px]' style={{
          background: `linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 18, 18, 0) -21.78%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 68.07%), url(${clubsBGimage})`,
          backgroundPosition: 'top center',
          backgroundSize: 'cover'

          // backgroundAttachment: 'fixed',
        }}>
          <Text type={'h2'} class='mt-14 max-md:mt-10'>About Us</Text>
          <Text type={'base'} class='mt-3 text-center max-md:w-[90%]' >Pioneering Excellence: Embracing our mission for a brighter tomorrow</Text>
          <!-- <a href="https://admissions.glentreeacademy.com" target='_blank'>
            <Button class='mt-3'>Apply Now</Button>
          </a> -->
        </div>

        
        <div class='w-full flex flex-row flex-wrap px-[136px] py-16 gap-5 x-md:px-4 max-md:py-6' style={{
          background: 'linear-gradient(180deg, #000000 0%, #142C1E 108.48%)'
        }}>
          <Text type={'h2'} class='text-white'>From the founder's desk</Text>
          <div class='flex flex-row w-full mt-8 items-center'>
            <div class='w-[360px] h-[410px] mr-[60px] shrink-0 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden'>
              <img src={vittal} alt="" class='w-full h-full object-cover' />
            </div>
            <div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='text-white'>Vittal Bhandary</Text>
              <Text type={'subtitle'} class='mt-1 font-normal'>CEO</Text>
              <Text type={'base'} class='mt-6'>Glentree Academy envisions a transformative approach to education, addressing the shortcomings of traditional learning. As a child, I found little joy in the stress of memorisation, yet I thrived in the immersive world of sports. Inspired by my own experiences and Preeti's vision of a happy learning environment, Glentree aims to create a place where children can freely explore their talents and passions without the burden of grades.</Text>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='flex flex-row w-full mt-8 items-center'>
            <div class='w-[360px] h-[410px] mr-[60px] shrink-0 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden'>
              <img src={preeti} alt="" class='w-full h-full object-cover' />
            </div>
            <div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='text-white'>Preeti Bhandary</Text>
              <Text type={'subtitle'} class='mt-1 font-normal'>DIRECTOR</Text>
              <Text type={'base'} class='mt-6'>Research shows that involved parents contribute to happier, healthier, and more successful children. However, in today's fast-paced world, lack of quality parenting time leads to increased pressure on children. We often neglect the present moment, consumed by daily crises. Engaging children in multiple activities is no substitute for parental presence, despite common misconceptions.</Text>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='flex flex-row w-full mt-8 items-center'>
            <div class='w-[360px] h-[410px] mr-[60px] shrink-0 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden'>
              <img src={sowmia} alt="" class='w-full h-full object-cover' />
            </div>
            <div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='text-white'>Sowmia Raguraman</Text>
              <Text type={'subtitle'} class='mt-1 font-normal'>MENTOR PRINCIPAL</Text>
              <Text type={'base'} class='mt-6'>As an educator, my goal is to nurture a growth mindset in children, teaching them to embrace failures as opportunities for progress. I strive to help them measure their advancement effectively, academically and personally. By encouraging a positive attitude towards change and letting go of past negative experiences, we can develop their mature thinking from an early age. This mindset enables them to persevere through setbacks, accept constructive criticism, refine their skills, and view mistakes as stepping stones to success.</Text>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>

        <div class='w-full flex flex-col flex-wrap px-20 py-16 gap-5 x-md:px-4 max-md:py-6 bg-white items-center'>
          <Text type={'h2'} class='text-black mb-4'>Our <span class='text-accent2'>Mission</span></Text>
          <div class='grid grid-rows-2 grid-cols-3 w-full gap-x-10 gap-y-7'>
            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Empowering<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Personal Growth
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>
            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Education with a<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Global Perspective
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>
            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Focus on igniting<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Lifelong Learning
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>
            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Always building<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Resilient Individuals
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>

            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Partnership between<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Parents - School
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>

            <div class='h-[400px] bg-red-100 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center p-5 flex flex-col justify-between' style={{
              backgroundImage: `linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(0,0,0, 0.6), rgba(0,0,0, 0.6)), url(${missionCardBG})`
            }}>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 self-end bg-contain bg-no-repeat" style={{ backgroundImage: `url("${cupIcon}")` }}></div>
              <Text type={'h3'} class='leading-tight text-[32px]'>Education always<br/>
                <span class='text-yellow'>
                  Improving
                </span>
              </Text>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        <BigAdmissionCTA />
        <Footer />
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
